SOLUTION
For everyone with the same issue. I solve the problem for me by adding the following code to the ServiceProvider (boot):
```

        if(app()-&gt;environment(&#39;testing&#39;)){
            $modules = array_slice(scandir(__DIR__.&quot;/../../Modules&quot;),2);
            foreach ($modules as $module){
                            app()-&gt;register( &quot;\Modules\\{$module}\\Providers\\{$module}ServiceProvider&quot;);

            }
        }
```

